     2. Style includes & FOUC suppression
     3. Top credits link
     4. Form helpers (toggle closures)
     5. Settings panel sections (Behavior / Display / Header / Spin)
     6. Action bar (Apply / Reset / Done)
     7. Footer row (support + version)
     8. Credits modal markup
     9. Inline JavaScript (section collapse, AJAX apply, reset, modal)
